introduction: Part of Love” is the first “situation series” on Thailand’s television history, which will provide you with beautiful scene like “series” style in a fun and comic story like “sitcom”. Story of all characters will be present in all point of views, charming with local Thai vocabulary, love and relationship among teenager, inspiration and spiritual of Thai youth etc.
